      <title>美联储巴尔表示监管机构正在关注商业房地产风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/fed-s-barr-says-regulators-eyeing-cre-risk-downgrade-more-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储首席银行监管机构表示，美国监管机构“密切关注”商业房地产贷款的风险，并在其财务面临新压力的情况下加大了对贷款机构监管评级的下调力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-16/fed-s-barr-says-regulators-eyeing-cre-risk-downgrade-more-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 14:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于战争风险和利率前景，石油价格处于年内最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价几乎没有变化，因为交易员权衡了中东日益紧张的局势与高于预期的美国通胀数据，这削弱了降息的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 23:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
